comments: Davis (LAL) contests Carter Jr.'s (ORL) jump shot, any contact on the follow through is consider incidental.
Carter Jr. (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Davis (LAL).
Russell (LAL) establishes himself in Wagner's (ORL) path and releases away from the screen as he rolls towards the basket.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Anthony's (ORL) path and does not deliver contact.
Banchero (ORL) jumps towards Reaves' (LAL) during his close out and initiates contact to Reaves' body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Reaves' (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as Reaves' defends under the screen.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Russell's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) engages and disengages with Schroder (LAL) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Schroder (LAL) moves to defend the shot.
Davis (LAL) moves alongside Wagner's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Gabriel (LAL) brings his arm toward Banchero's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Banchero's drive.
Banchero (ORL) and Reaves (LAL) come together off ball and marginal contact occurs as they disengage from one another.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Reaves' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as he defends under the pick.
Fultz (ORL) is moving alongside Reaves' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Reaves's (LAL) drive.
Fultz (ORL) moves laterally into Reaves' (LAL) path and initiates body contact that affects Reaves' SQBR during the drive.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Gabriel's (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage from the screen.
Gabriel (LAL) defends the drive and retreats his arm into a vertical position while defending Banchero's (ORL) shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Vanderblit (LAL) makes contact with the ball after Wagner's (ORL) gather and cleanly dislodges the ball before incidental arm contact occurs.
Gabriel (LAL) legally contests Houstan's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (LAL) jumps alongside Wagner (ORL) and marginal body contact occurs during Wagner's (ORL) step through and shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
Banchero (ORL) establishes himself in Vanderbilt's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Anthony (ORL) briefly grasps Reaves' (LAL) arm as they come together underneath the basket and immediately slides his hand off  as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to ORL.
Carter Jr. (ORL) brings his arm toward Reaves (LAL) and marginal contact occurs as Carter Jr. (ORL) releases away from the contact.
